							Privacy Policy
						</h1>
					</div>
					<div class="main__content">
						<p>FavFul is committed to protecting the privacy of our users. We sometimes collect personal information from our users. FavFul maintains the confidentiality, security and integrity of personal information that we obtain from our users. We do not disclose personal information to any outside party.</p>

						<p>When registering for FavFul.com or any of its related services, we ask you to provide certain personal information. This information is for internal use only and will not be distributed or sold to any parties outside FavFul. We strive to create contests and content which require a very minimal amount of information from our users. Our online surveys and contests sometimes ask users for contact information (like their email addresses) or information about their hobbies or interests. This information is also only for internal purposes and will not be shared with any party outside FavFul. </p>

						<p>You should be aware that when you are on FavFul.com you might be directed to other apps that are beyond our control. Every app on the web has a different privacy policy and different policies regarding your personal information. The privacy policies and the practices of apps outside of FavFul.com and all of its services are beyond our control. It is your responsibility to read and understand the privacy policies of any and all websites and apps you visit on the world wide web/app store. These other apps may send their own cookies to users, or otherwise collect data or solicit personal information. Always be aware of where you end up on the web. </p>

						<p>By using this app, you signify your assent to the FavFul privacy policy. If you do not agree to this policy, please do not use our app. Your continued use of our app following posted changes to these terms will mean that you accept those changes. You can send email to us with any further questions. </p>

						<p>At FavFul, we recognize your right to confidentiality and are committed to protecting your privacy. We use the information we collect on our app to provide you with a superior experience. When you register, we will ask you to set up an account, which includes your name, e-mail address and optionally your mailing address and various beauty related questions. In addition, we ask that you indicate whether you would like to receive e-mail from FavFul or sponsors or partners keeping you informed of news or features. </p>

						<p>We protect your account information against unauthorized access or release. We may share non-personal, summary, or aggregate data with partners and other third parties.</p>
